org.jscsi.target.scsi.modeSense

Class ModeParameterList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jscsi.target.scsi.modeSense.ModeParameterList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IResponseData, ISerializable

    public final class ModeParameterList
extends Object
implements IResponseData
    The mode parameter list contains a header, followed by zero or more block descriptors, followed by zero or more variable-length mode pages.

    This class uses the builder pattern to minimize the number of constructors and to avoid constructor use with a lot of null parameters.

    Author:
    Andreas Ergenzinger
